block_list.title: Video Tutorial
block_list.body: This is Paper Plane 26 of our 100 Exotic Paper Airplane Challenge. The Bar Flyer designed by Paul Jackson. This is an origami plane folded from a square sheet. Enjoy!!! If you missed my last Exotic Paper Airplane "Paper Plane 025 : Flying Bat by Max Hulme", you could watch it at https://youtu.be/ilTQvF5xKRM Thanks For Watching! Wilson Lee @Heap Art
